## Project Name

CryptoSouls

## Category 

Application

## Project Description

CryptoSouls is an NFT minting and battling game. In it, souls of famous warriors can be minted as NFT's, complete with a set of 5 stats: Strength, Intelligence, Endurance, Charisma, and Luck.

Players can enlist their CryptoSouls in the Battle Arena, where they are matched up against other CryptoSouls. Battles consist of 3 rounds of random stat matchups, with the warrior having the higher stat the victor!

## Use of IPFS, Filecoin and Libp2p
• Assets and token data are uploaded to IPFS and used when minting the each CryptoSoul. It's the foundation for the NFT's used in the game and secondary economy.

## Project Status

Under development

## Target Audience
• The target audience is gamers using Ethereum and people who have gotten involved in crypto collectables.

